"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Abbas Araghchi says the US attacks each time there is a diplomatic solution on the table. This happens as the two countries accuse each other of breaking ceasefires during celebrations of the Soviet Union's victory over Nazi Germany.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Attacks During Diplomatic Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Abbas Araghchi dice que Estados Unidos ataca cada vez que hay una soluci\u00f3n diplom\u00e1tica. Esto pasa mientras los dos pa\u00edses se acusan de romper treguas durante las celebraciones de la victoria de la Uni\u00f3n Sovi\u00e9tica sobre la Alemania nazi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques de EE.UU. en Charlas Diplom\u00e1ticas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nearly a month ago, P\u00e9ter Magyar led his Tisza party to a big win, ending 16 years of rule by Viktor Orb\u00e1n.\",            \"english_title\": \"P\u00e9ter Magyar's Big Win\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hace casi un mes, P\u00e9ter Magyar llev\u00f3 a su partido Tisza a una gran victoria, terminando con 16 a\u00f1os de gobierno de Viktor Orb\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gran Victoria de P\u00e9ter Magyar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A hacking group broke into the academic software Canvas, which is used by many schools and universities around the world.\",            \"english_title\": \"Canvas Hacked\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un grupo de hackers entr\u00f3 en el software acad\u00e9mico Canvas, que es usado por muchas escuelas y universidades en el mundo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hackeo de Canvas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Some people on the Spanish island are worried that the arrival of the MV Hondius could be a health risk.\",            \"english_title\": \"Health Concerns on Spanish Island\",            \"translated_version\": \"Algunas personas en la isla espa\u00f1ola est\u00e1n preocupadas de que la llegada del MV Hondius pueda ser un riesgo para la salud.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaciones de Salud en Isla Espa\u00f1ola\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Greek media report that a drone, which might have had explosives, could be either Ukrainian or related to the Russia-Ukraine war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone with Explosives\",            \"translated_version\": \"Medios griegos informan que un dron, que podr\u00eda tener explosivos, podr\u00eda ser ucraniano o estar relacionado con la guerra Rusia-Ucrania.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Dron con Explosivos\"        }    ]}"